----------------------------------------------------------------------
Attribution
----------------------------------------------------------------------
This dataset is a derivative ("stressed") version of:

  Statlog (German Credit Data)
  UCI Machine Learning Repository
  https://archive.ics.uci.edu/dataset/144/statlog+german+credit+data

The original records are preserved; controlled, documented perturbations
were applied to a subset of the observed inputs. Please attribute both the
original source and Santander AI Lab when using this dataset.
